year: 2026
license: CC-BY-4.0
abstract: >-
  Replication dataset for the paper "A Taxonomy of Real-World
  Asset Tokenization for Blockchain-Based Financial
  Infrastructure". Contains a 23-attribute taxonomy across five
  components (Governance, Asset, Token Properties, DLT, Economy),
  the classification of the 20 largest RWA tokenization protocols
  by market capitalization, per-assignment source citations, and
  the DeFiLlama sample-selection snapshot.
keywords:
  - real-world assets
  - asset tokenization
  - RWA
  - decentralized finance
  - tokenized securities
  - smart contracts
  - taxonomy
